# infra_coding_101/01_Challenge

Goal: become able to do very basic stuff using a declarative infrastructure language/tool.
Allowed tools: Windows DSC, Puppet, Ansible, Chef, Salt and CfEngine.
Tasks:
  a) Create a new user
  b) Install a software
  c) Manage a file content
  d) Bring a service up
Expected: the code for each task using the allowed tools.



